highlights.text: “Sonho de Todo Casal - Ao Vivo” by Marcos & Belutti is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Brazil, up 77 spots at #96.
“Lapada Dela - Ao Vivo” by Grupo Menos É Mais and Matheus Fernandes has been on Top Songs Brazil the longest, at 940 days straight.
Henrique & Juliano has the most spots on Top Songs Brazil. “Última Saudade - Ao Vivo” is the highest at #13.
“ACENDE UM ISQUEIRO” by Lu & Rayane and Panda is the highest new entry on Top Songs Brazil at #163.
